EN: The children were asked to trace back their childhood memories and write them down.

ZH: 回溯过去的科学研究，我们可以看到人类的进步和发展。
EN: Looking back at past scientific research, we can see the progress and development of humanity.

ZH: 在艺术领域，回溯艺术家的生平可以深入了解他们的创作动机。
